```plantuml
@startuml IBM_customer-sentiment-on-seller-quality-nlu-cp4d

actor User

User -> JupyterNotebook: Start Analysis
JupyterNotebook -> Db2Database: Load Customer Review Data
Db2Database -> JupyterNotebook: Return Refined Data

JupyterNotebook -> WatsonNLU: Perform Sentiment Analysis
WatsonNLU -> JupyterNotebook: Return Sentiment Scores

JupyterNotebook -> JupyterNotebook: Calculate Seller Quality Ratings

JupyterNotebook -> EmbeddedDashboardService: Prepare Data for Visualization
EmbeddedDashboardService -> User: Display Interactive Dashboard

@enduml
```